    "updated_at": "2015-11-08T13:14:15Z",
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "In the long term we probably want FrozenActorLayer to register a callback against `Shroud.CellsChanged` and only tick the frozen actor when the visibility near it changes.  This would give us a decent perf improvement overall (by not ticking most actors), counteracting the slower individual ticks.\n"
